title: Ep 2509 - Wheres Jethalal?
shortDesc: Champaklal is unsure about Jethalal's whereabouts and creates panic among Gokuldham society members by sharing the details of his dream. The attempts made to reach Jethalal prove futile.

title: Ep 2510 - Off to Senorica Island
shortDesc: Champaklal along with Tappu, Taarak Mehta and Popatlal decide to go to Senorica Island to find Jethalal.

title: Ep 2511 - The Gifts
shortDesc: Jethalal explains to Champaklal the reason he didn't answer the phone. After knowing that Jethalal lost his phone, Champaklal calms down. Then, Jethalal surprises the Gokuldham society members by showering them with gifts.

title: Ep 2512 - The Scam
shortDesc: The entire Gokuldham society is in a relaxed mood after the entire charade revolving around Jethalal and Senorita Island is over. But Patrakar Popatlal stirs up the entire society when he comes and shows everyone the latest bank scam.

title: Ep 2513 - Bhide Is Worried
shortDesc: Bhide with all the men of Gokuldham society visits the Sahi-Salaamat Bank after reading a news about all the scams happening in various banks as he is worried about his money in the bank.

title: Ep 2514 - Fresh Trouble for Jethalal
shortDesc: Jethalal engages in a battle with Bhide to solve a few riddles. Bhide solves the riddles thrown at him by Jethalal but Jethalal, knowing that he can't solve the riddle, avoids giving the answer altogether.

title: Ep 2515 - The Trouble Continues
shortDesc: The hostage situation continues in Gada electronics as the kidnappers take Nattu Kaka with them and Bagha Bhai tries to keep Jethalal busy and doesn't let him go to the godown.

title: Ep 2516 - Whats Inside the Warehouse?
shortDesc: Baga tries to prevent Jethalal from going inside the warehouse. Then, Babita arrives at Gada Electronics to make a purchase for Iyer. Jethalal insists that Baga open the warehouse so that Babita can have a seat.

title: Ep 2517 - The Love Letter
shortDesc: The kidnapper reveals to Jethalal and Bagha that he abducted a writer to help him write a love letter for a girl he likes and Jethalal is shocked to see that the writer the kidnapper abducted is none other than Taarak Mehta.

title: Ep 2518 - Love Wins
shortDesc: The girl whom the kidnapper sent the love letter written by Jethalal, comes to the basement of Gada Electronics and then confesses her love for him. Everyone is surprised to see Jethalal's letter doing wonders.

title: Ep 2519 - An Ode To Gada Electronics
shortDesc: Taarak narrates his kidnapping incident to Gokuldham society members and informs them that it was the letter written by Jethalal that saved him. Then, Jethalal reads out the letter and is appreciated by the society members.

title: Ep 2520 - The Big Surprise
shortDesc: Guests arrive at Gokuldham society and meet the society members. The guests inform the society members that they have to assemble in the  Club House at 8:30 as a big surprise is awaiting them. What is this surprise? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 2521 - Surprise, Surprise!
shortDesc: The Gokuldham society members are confused over the big surprise planned at the clubhouse. Bhide thinks Jethalal has planned a surprise, and that too without his consent.

title: Ep 2522 - The Journey
shortDesc: All the members of the Gokuldham society gather in the clubhouse for the big surprise but are confused as no one from the society invited them.

title: Ep 2523 - The Celebration
shortDesc: Members of Gokuldham society remember and celebrate their journey of ten years in Gokuldham style and enjoy their time with each other and also thank the audience.
